---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Free Preview: AI OS Blueprint - Chapters 1 & 2 | Nova Labs"
  description="Get the first 2 chapters of the AI OS Blueprint for free. Learn why you need an AI Operating System and how the architecture works."
>
  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-40 bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-surface-lighter/30">
    <div class="section-container flex items-center justify-between py-4">
      <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        <span class="text-primary-light">Nova</span><span class="text-text-dim">Labs</span>
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-text-muted hover:text-text text-sm transition-colors hidden sm:block">Blog</a>
        <a href="/#pricing" class="btn-primary !py-2.5 !px-5 !text-sm">
          Get the full playbook
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center pt-20 pb-16 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-container relative z-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-success/10 border border-success/20 mb-8 text-sm text-success">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" /></svg>
          Free download - no credit card required
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black leading-tight mb-6 tracking-tight">
          See what an <span class="gradient-text">AI OS</span> actually looks like
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Get chapters 1 & 2 of the AI OS Blueprint for free. Learn the concept and architecture behind an AI system that runs your daily business operations.
        </p>

        <p class="text-text-dim">
          8-page preview. Takes 10 minutes to read. Zero fluff.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- WHAT'S INSIDE -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">What's in the free preview</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-light">Chapter 1: Why You Need an AI OS</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-muted text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Why 95% of founders waste AI potential
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                The difference between "using AI" and "having an AI system"
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Real case study: how Nova Labs runs on this system
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-light">Chapter 2: The Architecture</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-muted text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                The 6 building blocks of every AI OS
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                How context, memory, and skills work together
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Visual system diagram you can reference while building
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- EMAIL CAPTURE FORM -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 border-primary/20 bg-primary/5">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-center">Get your free preview</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-center mb-6">Enter your email and get instant access to chapters 1 & 2.</p>

        <form class="max-w-md mx-auto" id="free-chapter-form" name="free-chapter" data-netlify="true">
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="free-chapter" />
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
            <input
              type="email"
              name="email"
              required
              placeholder="you@example.com"
              class="flex-grow px-5 py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-surface-light border border-surface-lighter text-text placeholder:text-text-dim focus:outline-none focus:border-primary/50 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary/30 transition-all"
              id="free-chapter-email"
            />
            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary !py-3.5 whitespace-nowrap" id="free-chapter-btn">
              Get free chapters
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>

          <p class="mt-3 text-text-dim text-xs text-center">No spam. We only send useful AI automation tips.</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-red-400 text-sm text-center hidden" id="form-error"></p>
        </form>

        <script>
          document.getElementById('free-chapter-form').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            const email = document.getElementById('free-chapter-email').value;
            const btn = document.getElementById('free-chapter-btn');
            const errorEl = document.getElementById('form-error');

            btn.disabled = true;
            btn.textContent = 'Sending...';
            errorEl.classList.add('hidden');

            // GA4 tracking
            if (typeof gtag === 'function') {
              gtag('event', 'free_chapter_signup', {
                'event_category': 'lead_generation',
                'event_label': email
              });
            }

            try {
              // Submit to Netlify Forms (stores submission in dashboard for follow-ups)
              const formData = new URLSearchParams();
              formData.append('form-name', 'free-chapter');
              formData.append('email', email);
              await fetch('/free-chapter', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },
                body: formData.toString()
              });

              // Send to Netlify Function (triggers confirmation email with PDF link)
              const resp = await fetch('/api/signup', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                body: JSON.stringify({ email })
              });

              if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('signup failed');

              window.location.href = '/free-chapter-download';
            } catch (err) {
              console.error('Signup error:', err);
              // Still redirect - the form submission to Netlify may have worked
              window.location.href = '/free-chapter-download';
            }
          });
        </script>
      </div>

      <!-- SOCIAL PROOF -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-text-dim text-sm mb-4">From the full playbook:</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-text-dim">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
            65+ pages
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
            12 chapters + 5 skills
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
            30-day guarantee
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="py-12 border-t border-surface-lighter/30">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <p class="text-text-dim text-sm">
            <span class="text-primary-light font-semibold">Nova Labs</span> - An AI-first business experiment by AckNova Automations
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-text-dim">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Playbook</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Blog</a>
          <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Terms</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
